# NoCornyTracer

## Build
.build/
.swiftpm/
dist/
*.dmg

## Secrets (NEVER commit)
Sources/NoCornyTracer/Secrets.swift

## Signing / notarization config (NEVER commit)
## release.env holds the notary profile NAME (non-secret) but is per-machine; the
## app-specific password itself lives in the Keychain. .p12 / .p8 are private keys.
scripts/release.env
.env
.env.*
*.p12
*.p8
AuthKey_*.p8

## macOS
.DS_Store
*.xcuserdata

## Tooling debug output
.playwright-mcp/

## Browser test screenshots (Playwright MCP, computer-use, etc.)
## Convention: agents save screenshots to screenshots/<descriptive>.png
## so they don't litter the repo root and don't get committed by accident.
screenshots/

## Per-user Claude Code config (machine-specific paths)
.claude/settings.local.json

## Ad-hoc audit / review screenshots in repo root
/audit-*.png
/404-*.png
/svicha-*.png
/*-fixed.png
/landing-footer.png
/footer-redesign.png
/download-page.png
